Text: Before you start criticizing Americans you might want to check these pictures again; #s 2 & 5 were obviously not taken in the US, my guess is 2 was taken in S. Korea and 5 in The Phillipines. #4 is suspect and #s 3 & 7 have no geographical reference at all!

The audacity of insulting Americans when you yourself likely come from a country which now emulates our laws, freedoms, and liberties speaks much to the IQ of yourself and your own countrymen. 

That being said, stupid fucking retards exist everywhere, as your post clarifies.
dougaldog is right on those. #4 looks to be a zebra crossing, not a crosswalk. #6, I'm sad to say,  is a buckeye plate on the back, so maybe one out of seven, maybe two of seven are American pics....
